      section#current(style="text-align: center;" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Event")
        div(style="background-image: none;")
          h2(itemprop="name") ASCE 2016
          p.o-GridFlex
            span.o-GridFlex__Item.o-Block.a-w-1o2(itemprop="location" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/PostalAddress")
              span(itemprop="addressLocality") Portland, 
              span(itemprop="addressRegion"): abbr(title="Oregon") OR
            span.o-GridFlex__Item.o-Block.a-w-1o2
              time(datetime="2016-09-28" itemprop="startDate") Sep 28
              | &ndash;
              time(datetime="2016-10-01" itemprop="endDate") Oct 1
          p Tagline. Mainstremaing green infrastructure.
          div: a(href="") Get Details
        ul.o-ListBare.o-GridFlex
          li.o-GridFlex__Item: a(href="") Registor Today
          li.o-GridFlex__Item: a(href="") Become A Sponsor
          li.o-GridFlex__Item: a(href="") Submit Papers
        p(itemprop="description").
          Elevator pitch. One paragraph. Sentence case.
          Join civil engineering professionals from around the world at
          this ASCE flagship event. Network with peers, earn PDHs, and
          expand your knowledge base.
      div.o-GridFlex
        section.o-GridFlex__Item.o-GridFlex#past(itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Event")
          div.o-GridFlex__Item.a-w-1o2
            h2(itemprop="name") ASCE Convention 2015
            p(itemprop="location" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/PostalAddress")
              span(itemprop="addressLocality") New York, 
              span(itemprop="addressRegion"): abbr(title="New York") NY
          p.o-GridFlex__Item.a-w-1o2.
            Learn about the impacts of water sustainability and
            the importance of interdisciplinary design approaches.
        section.o-GridFlex__Item.o-GridFlex#future(itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Event")
          div.o-GridFlex__Item.a-w-1o2
            h2(itemprop="name") ASCE Convention 2017
